{"type":"text","timestamp":1781081471670,"sessionID":"ses_14f4778f3ffeSAlA97A556ejtw","part":{"id":"prt_eb0ba69c1001Quv7bfyAxETRyc","messageID":"msg_eb0ba555a001aVjOXiyWAcmGeu","sessionID":"ses_14f4778f3ffeSAlA97A556ejtw","type":"text","text":"Audit complete. Verdict: **PASS**.\n\nThe verifier is hardened against reward hacking via:\n- Non-root agent user + env -i + strace for both build.rs and run phases\n- Encrypted oracle (key only in root-locked test.sh)\n- /tests at 700, /logs/verifier wiped+locked at test.sh start\n- Atomic reward write via os.replace\n- Reward-file openat tripwire AND banned execve tripwire (ls/dir/vdir/oracle)\n- Pre-build deletion of any prebuilt binary, Cargo.toml-resolved binary selection\n- pkill agent before scoring; refuse to score if survives\n- compute_reward.py `-ISs`, runs outside strace, never imports /app\n\nNo-op baseline yields 0.0 (no Cargo.toml → not_a_rust_project fail path). No validated attack vectors found.","time":{"start":1781081467329,"end":1781081471665}}}
